  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Kdepim</title>
 <para>Installez <application>Kdepim</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes :</para>
<screen>
<userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir;         -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc                 -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release                 -DCMAKE_MINIMUM_REQUIRED_VERSION=3.0       -Wno-dev .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput>
</screen>
    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput>
</screen>
  </sect2>
